Package net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.sensing

Class Sensor<E extends net.minecraft.world.entity.LivingEntity>

java.lang.Object
net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.sensing.Sensor<E extends net.minecraft.world.entity.LivingEntity>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of entity that can use this sensor.
public abstract class Sensor<E extends net.minecraft.world.entity.LivingEntity>  extends Object
Represents an abstract class for a Sensor. Sensors run actions on a tick timer, and depend on what memories currently exist.
